# Knowledge files (may contain sensitive RMIT content)
# README + FAQ corpus + the published process-writing standards are allowed.
# Anything else dropped into knowledge/ (e.g. internal-only drafts) stays out.
knowledge/*
!knowledge/README.txt
!knowledge/process-faqs.md
!knowledge/RMIT - Tips for process writing.docx
!knowledge/Nintex Process writing techniques.docx
!knowledge/VERB_LIST_CATEGORISED.docx
